        "content": "<p>Hey all,<br>\nThis is the discussion thread of Bart Jacobs' talk, \"De Finetti's construction as a categorical limit\".<br>\nThe talk, besides being on Zoom, is livestreamed here: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/wsSpaIWqszQ\">https://youtu.be/wsSpaIWqszQ</a></p>\n<div class=\"youtube-video message_inline_image\"><a data-id=\"wsSpaIWqszQ\" href=\"https://youtu.be/wsSpaIWqszQ\"><img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/wsSpaIWqszQ/default.jpg\"></a></div>",
